OL,3,CMan accused of stalking Dame Penny
OL,4,CMordaunt 'only wanted to congratulate
OL,5,Cher'
OL,7,FA 61-year-old man accused of stalking
OL,8,Fformer Conservative Party leadership
OL,9,Fcandidate Dame Penny Mordaunt told
OL,10,Fpolice that his actions were
OL,11,F"harmless" and he had only wanted to
OL,12,F"shake her hand" and "congratulate"
OL,13,Fher.
OL,15,FEdward Brandt, of Freshwater, Isle of
OL,16,FWight, is accused of one charge of
OL,17,Fstalking intending to cause serious
OL,18,Falarm or distress against the former
OL,19,FMP for Portsmouth North between 11
OL,20,FSeptember 2023 and 12 May 2024.
