OL,3,CMan accused of stalking Dame Penny
OL,4,CMordaunt 'only wanted to congratulate
OL,5,Cher'
OL,7,FThe jury at Southampton Crown Court
OL,8,Fhas heard that Mr Brandt sent multiple
OL,9,Femails and phone messages to Ms
OL,10,FMordaunt, as well as turning up at her
OL,11,FPortsmouth office out of hours in a
OL,12,Fbid to meet her.
OL,14,FThe court was told that Mr Brandt was
OL,15,Farrested on 24 March 2024 and given a
OL,16,Fconditional caution on 19 April 2024,
OL,17,Frequiring him not to contact Dame
OL,18,FPenny, but he then left two voicemail
OL,19,Fmessages for her on 6 and 11 May.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
