OL,3,CMan accused of stalking Dame Penny
OL,4,CMordaunt 'only wanted to congratulate
OL,5,Cher'
OL,7,FIn one of the messages, Mr Brandt
OL,8,Fsaid: "I am going to go on gently
OL,9,Fknocking at your door in order to
OL,10,Fshake your hand, I am not giving up."
OL,12,FHe also failed to comply with other
OL,13,Fterms of the conditional caution,
OL,14,Fwhich required him to complete a
OL,15,Fvictim awareness course, the trial
OL,16,Fheard.
OL,18,FHe was made subject to an interim
OL,19,Fstalking protection order at Isle of
OL,20,FWight Magistrates' Court on 16 July
OL,21,F2024.
