OL,4,CMordaunt 'only wanted to congratulate
OL,5,Cher'
OL,7,FDame Penny said in a statement to
OL,8,Fpolice that she "feared sexual
OL,9,Fviolence" because of the defendant's
OL,10,F"creepy" behaviour, the court has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FIn a police interview after Mr Brandt
OL,14,Fwas arrested on 12 May, he said that
OL,15,Fhe had tried to contact her again in
OL,16,Fthe two voice messages because he
OL,17,Fwanted to "set the record straight".
