OL,3,CMan accused of stalking Dame Penny
OL,4,CMordaunt 'only wanted to congratulate
OL,5,Cher'
OL,7,FHe said: "I am not about to commit
OL,8,Fphysical violence or sexual assault, I
OL,9,Fjust want to shake her hand and
OL,10,Fcongratulate her. It's a mighty big
OL,11,Fsledgehammer to smash a tiny nut."
OL,13,FHe added: "Everything she said in that
OL,14,Fstatement was wholly, wholly
OL,15,Finaccurate.
OL,17,F"I just want to explain to her what
OL,18,Fshe said was completely untrue, (there
OL,19,Fwas) no malice whatsoever, it's
OL,20,Fcompletely harmless, friendly,
OL,21,Fcongratulatory, 'Well done you'."
