OL,7,FHe added: "She's getting other people
OL,8,Fto do her dirty work for her."
OL,10,FHe also said: "My interest is purely
OL,11,Fpolitical, purely congratulatory,
OL,12,F'well done you', I wanted to get a
OL,13,Fsigned copy of her book, it's a
OL,14,Fmountain out of a mole hill."
