OL,3,CMan accused of stalking Dame Penny
OL,4,CMordaunt 'only wanted to congratulate
OL,5,Cher'
OL,7,FEarlier, the court heard that Mr
OL,8,FBrandt pushed his way through a
OL,9,Fsecurity gate at Lakeside business
OL,10,Fpark in Portsmouth where Dame Penny
OL,11,Fhad her constituency office on the
OL,12,Fafternoon of Saturday, 16 December
OL,13,F2023.
OL,15,FNeil Tombs, a security officer, told
OL,16,Fthe court that he saw Mr Brandt
OL,17,Fscanning a list of companies and said
OL,18,Fhe saw him push through the barrier,
OL,19,Fsetting off an alarm.
