OL,3,CMan accused of stalking Dame Penny
OL,4,CMordaunt 'only wanted to congratulate
OL,5,Cher'
OL,7,FThe court heard that Dame Penny was in
OL,8,Fher office at the time, even though it
OL,9,Fwas the weekend.
OL,11,FMr Tombs said: "After I shouted 'Oi,
OL,12,Fstop' and I started running, at that
OL,13,Ftime he wasn't far from any office, I
OL,14,Fwas trying to stop him going any
OL,15,Ffurther.
OL,17,F"He turned around and looked at me
OL,18,Fthat time. He started asking me
OL,19,Fquestions about Penny Mordaunt, that's
OL,20,Fwhen I realised her office wasn't that
OL,21,Ffar away.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
