OL,3,CMan accused of stalking Dame Penny
OL,4,CMordaunt 'only wanted to congratulate
OL,5,Cher'
OL,7,F"I remember him asking when is she
OL,8,Fhere, I said 'Monday to Friday only'
OL,9,Fand 'you need an appointment to see
OL,10,Fanyone here, not just Penny Mordaunt'."
OL,12,FHe said he then escorted him out of
OL,13,Fthe building.
OL,15,FMr Brandt denies the charge and the
OL,16,Ftrial continues.
